{
  "text": "Then equation [CITATION_1] shows that q(k) is the average of q(k, \u03c3) over all \u03c3. To complete the proof of Lemma 3.1, it suffices to show that for each permutation \u03c3, inequality (3) holds with q(k, \u03c3) in place of q(k).",
